    <PrimAttribute name="baseTimeToChkpt" id="9b459de0-e697-462c-b65a-ed5f125b63fe">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>This is the time from the base time to the checkpoint
(and is relative to the direction of travel). 
For example: For an ARRIVAL, with the basetime at the WHARF,
the time will be -15mins (ie. Time at Tanea is 
15 mins earlier than the time at the wharf for an arrival).
For departure with base time at wharf, time will be +15</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
